beer.beer_description:
For BOS we selected some of our favourite dual-purpose hops, often overlooked in Hazy IPA's, and placed them front and centre.

Bright citrus peel, pine needles & tree sap are all flavours we love in WCIPA’s, turns out we also love them in a NEIPA
